title: Provided further that in case of Public Sector Undertaking the premium for FSI beyond Zonal (basic) FSI shall be payable as decided by Govt
clause_text: Provided further that in case of Public Sector Undertaking the premium for FSI beyond Zonal (basic) FSI shall be payable as decided by Govt. from time to time.
section: 33(3) Buildings of Government/MCGM/Statutory Bodies, Semi- Government and PSU Offices:
